eedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dce1719410891268.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dce1719410891268.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dce1719410891268.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vud1665702751551\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vud1665702751551__eject_216777\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Eject a page when printing.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vud1665702751551__topic_d71360e1_d71361e1_d71362e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vud1665702751551__p_d71363e1_d71364e1_d71365e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vud1665702751551__topic_d46902e1_d46903e1_d46904e1_d46905e1_d46906e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d370677e65\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1__entry__1\">\n -1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6434e1_d6435e1_d6436e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span> was successful.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1404\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_NO_PRINTING&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vud1665702751551__table_d6437e1_d6438e1_d6439e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Not printing (that is, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$printing</span> is 0). The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span> statement is ignored.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vud1665702751551__topic_d46907e1_d46908e1_d46909e1_d46910e1_d46911e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d370677e189\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vud1665702751551__p_d71372e1_d71373e1_d71374e1\">Use in Form and Report components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vud1665702751551__p_d71375e1_d71376e1_d71377e1\">Not allowed in the getFocus trigger of a header or footer frame.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vud1665702751551__topic_d46912e1_d46913e1_d46914e1_d46915e1_d46916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d370677e201\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vud1665702751551__p_d71381e1_d71382e1_d71383e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span> statement forces a page break and causes Uniface to continue printing on the following page. It is recommended to place the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span> statement in either the getFocus trigger or leavePrinted of an entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vud1665702751551__p_d71384e1_d71385e1_d71386e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span> statement is ignored in the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vud1665702751551__li_d32039e1_d32040e1_d32041e1\">Uniface is not printing (that is, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$printing</span> is 0).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vud1665702751551__li_d32042e1_d32043e1_d32044e1\">In the second or later occurrence of an entity that is painted with horizontal repetition.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vud1665702751551__li_d32045e1_d32046e1_d32047e1\">On an empty page.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vud1665702751551__li_d32048e1_d32049e1_d32050e1\">In the getFocus trigger of a header or footer frame.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vud1665702751551__section_b4t_qcc_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d370677e241\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">eject</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example starts a new page when the contents of the INVDATE\n            field change:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"vud1665702751551__pre_lrd_rcc_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger leavePrinted \n compare/next (INVDATE) from \"INVOICE\" ;test if next date the same (or exists)\n if ($result = 0) ;if next date exists and not the same\n eject  ;start printing on new page\n endif\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zdt1665702751625.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>skip</a><p>Skip the specified number of lines when printing.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mfh1719680957014.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$printing</a><p>Return a status indicating whether the current component is printing.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420114\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420114\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "eject Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Eject a page when printing. eject Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Description -1 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 0 eject was successful. Table 2. Values commonly returned by $procerror following eject Value Error constant Meaning -1404 <UPROCERR_NO_PRINTING> Not printing (that is, $printing is 0). The eject statement is ignored. Use Use in Form and Report components. Not allowed in the getFocus trigger of a header or footer frame. Description The eject statement forces a page break and causes Uniface to continue printing on the following page. It is recommended to place the eject statement in either the getFocus trigger or leavePrinted of an entity. The eject statement is ignored in the following circumstances: Uniface is not printing (that is, $printing is 0). In the second or later occurrence of an entity that is painted with horizontal repetition. On an empty page. In the getFocus trigger of a header or footer frame. Example: Using eject The following example starts a new page when the contents of the INVDATE field change: trigger leavePrinted compare/next (INVDATE) from \"INVOICE\" ;test if next date the same (or exists) if ($result = 0) ;if next date exists and not the same eject ;start printing on new page endif end Copy Related Links skip Skip the specified number of lines when printing. $printing Return a status indicating whether the current component is printing. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}